description:
When you watch Revenge of the Sith, it's hard not to imagine: What If Anakin had made a different choice? We'd Iike to think that the light side of the Force would prevail and the galaxy would live at peace. But Palpatine wasn't the source of Anakin's darkness--he only cultivated it. How would Anakin  solve all the corruption in the senate? 

By taking Palaptine's place.
